  {title: "title", body: "<div class=\"top-quote-box quote\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<h2>3,000 homeless men &amp; women look to DESC for help every day</h2>\r\n<div class=\"medium-8 columns\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"donate-button medium-2 columns\"><a href=\"https://donatenow.networkforgood.org/DESC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Donate Now</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"medium-7 columns\">\r\n<div class=\"topic-heading\">\r\n<h1><a href=\"../2\">What We Do</a></h1>\r\n<h2 class=\"topic-heading\" style=\"line-height: 1.2em; color: #000000; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong>DESC continues to set the standard for excellence in supportive housing, winning local and national&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.4px; font-weight: normal;\" href=\"../../what_we_do\">recognition</a><span style=\"color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14.4px; background-color: #fefefe;\">&nbsp;for the effectiveness of its programs.</span></strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"learn-more\">\r\n<div class=\"learn-more-heading white\">\r\n<h4>Learn More</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"../3\">Who We Serve</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../4\">Entry Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: #fefefe; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" href=\"http://desc.org/housing.html\">Supportive Housing</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: #fefefe; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline-width: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" href=\"http://desc.org/employs.html\">Employment Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: #fefefe; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" href=\"http://desc.org/consultation.html\">Consultation</a></p>\r\n<p><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: #fefefe; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" href=\"http://desc.org/vulnerability.html\">Assessment Tool</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topic-summary medium-9 columns\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\">DESC provides effective and affordable solutions to homelessness for our community's most vulnerable single adults through a nationally recognized interwoven network of care, housing, and support, including:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem 1.25rem; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; line-height: 1.6; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #fefefe;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">383 emergency shelter beds at four locations</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">11 supportive housing sites totaling over 750 state-of-the-art apartments</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Over 200 'scattered site' apartments rented from private landlords and enriched with comprehensive case management services</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Placement of nearly 600 homeless adults into housing each year -- more than any other local provider</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">State-licensed mental health and outpatient substance use disorder treatment program</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">A comprehensive daytime service center which provides vocational training, veterans outreach, and hygiene facilities</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">A Program of Assertive Community Treatment (PACT) for men and women transitioning from long periods of institutionalization</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Long-term case management for homeless and formerly homeless adults living with persistent and severe mental illness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"medium-7 columns\">\r\n<h1><a href=\"../2\">Who We Are</a></h1>\r\n<div class=\"learn-more\">\r\n<div class=\"learn-more-heading white\">\r\n<h4>Learn More</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"../3\">Who We Serve</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../4\">Entry Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topic-summary medium-9 columns\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">DESC (Downtown Emergency Service Center) is a nonprofit organization of nearly 600 professional staff, board members, and community volunteers who strive to fulfill DESC's&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; color: #41887a; font-size: 12pt;\"><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"http://desc.org/mission.html\">mission</a></span>&nbsp;to end chronic homelessness in our community.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">We are your neighbors, friends, and family who&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; color: #41887a; font-size: 12pt;\"><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"http://desc.org/history.html\">since 1979</a></span>&nbsp;have sought justice, compassion and support for the most vulnerable members of our society.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">We are leaders in our field, an<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; color: #41887a;\">&nbsp;<a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 12pt;\" href=\"http://desc.org/leadership.html\">organization</a></span>&nbsp;of dedicated men and women for whom no job in the service of our clients is too daunting nor too menial</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">We are Seattle's leading provider of&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; color: #41887a; font-size: 12pt;\"><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"http://desc.org/awards.html\">award winning</a></span>&nbsp;housing and support services to chronically homeless adults who are living with mental illness, addictive disorders, and co-occurring disabilities</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mobile-spacing\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"medium-7 columns\">\r\n<div class=\"topic-heading\">\r\n<h1><a href=\"../2\">Learn More</a></h1>\r\n<h3>sub heading</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"learn-more\">\r\n<div class=\"learn-more-heading white\">\r\n<h4>Learn More</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"../3\">Who We Serve</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../4\">Entry Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topic-summary medium-9 columns\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #fefefe;\">On November 14, 2016, the Seattle Human Services Department (HSD) announced that DESC, in partnership with&nbsp;</span><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: #fefefe; line-height: inherit; color: #50844d; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\" href=\"https://www.oslserves.org/\">Operation Sack Lunch</a><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #fefefe;\">, has been selected to operate Seattle&rsquo;s Navigation Center site when it opens later this year. The center will provide an alternative model of indoor emergency shelter that will accomodate the unique needs facing people who are living unsheltered and in encampments. DESC will operate the 24-hour, low-barrier shelter while Operation Sack Lunch will provide food and meal support to those at the shelter.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"medium-7 columns\">\r\n<div class=\"topic-heading\">\r\n<h1><a href=\"../2\">Get Involved</a></h1>\r\n<h3>sub heading</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"learn-more\">\r\n<div class=\"learn-more-heading white\">\r\n<h4>Learn More</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"../3\">Who We Serve</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../4\">Entry Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topic-summary medium-9 columns\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ending homelessness is&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; line-height: inherit;\">not</strong>&nbsp;a mystery. Experience proves that placing homeless men and women in housing supported by trained staff with a complement of health care, chemical dependency treatment, and mental health services keeps even the most vulnerable and disabled adults off of the streets and safely housed.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">We also know that the type of programs offered by DESC actually cost less than allowing people to remain homeless. The result is fewer tax dollars spent.&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; line-height: inherit;\">Everyone benefits!</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\"><span class=\"smallheading\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 30px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #41887a; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you believe that homelessness can be eliminated, you can:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem 1.25rem; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; line-height: 1.6; color: #0a0a0a; font-size: 16px; background-color: #fefefe; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">donate</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">volunteer</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">attend an event</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">advocate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"col1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; width: 630px; float: left; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">If you have questions about making a donation or would like to speak to someone about making one, please contact&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; color: #41887a; font-size: 12pt;\"><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"mailto:mmayes@desc.org\">Megan Mayes</a></span>, Director of Development, at 206-515-1553.</p>\r\n<p class=\"col1\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; background-color: #fefefe; width: 630px; float: left; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"mobile-spacing\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"medium-7 columns\">\r\n<div class=\"topic-heading\">\r\n<h1><a href=\"../2\">Contact Us</a></h1>\r\n<h3>sub heading</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"learn-more\">\r\n<div class=\"learn-more-heading white\">\r\n<h4>Learn More</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"../3\">Who We Serve</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../4\">Entry Services</a></p>\r\n<p><a href=\"../5\">Clinical Services</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"topic-summary medium-9 columns\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\">Main Office: 515 Third Avenue, Seattle, WA 98104</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\">Phone: 206-464-1570</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\">Fax: 206-624-4196</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\">TDD/TDY callers can reach us via the Washington Relay Service, at (800) 833-6388</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\">Email:&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; color: #41887a; font-size: 12pt;\"><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; background-color: transparent; line-height: inherit; color: #41887a; text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\" href=\"mailto:info@desc.org\">info@desc.org</a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #333333; font-size: 14px;\">Fund Development Office</strong>: 206-464-1570 extension 3011 or 3445</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-rendering: optimizeLegibility; color: #0a0a0a; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fefefe;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; line-height: inherit; color: #333333; font-size: 14px;\">For media inquires</strong>, contact&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; color: #41887a; font-size: 12pt;\"><a class=\"greenlink\" style=\"